<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Laboratory Corp started.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Laboratory Corp started.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-06-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>Credit Suisse First Boston said it initiated coverage of Laboratory Corp of America with a hold rating.</p>
<p>-- said although it expects Laboratory Corp to report losses through the next year, the company's improved margins and a focus on reducing accounts receivable should strengthen the company's cash flow and help it pay down debt.</p>
<p>-- expects Laboratory Corp to report a net loss of $0.04 a share in 1997 and a loss of $0.03 a share in 1998.</p>
<p>-- Laboratory Corp was unchanged at 2-3/4.</p>
